column2: Hello! I am alive!

The network connection failed. Please try again later.
I will vacuum the hell out of this place.
Have you messed up this place again? Let me take care of it.
It is the time for cleaning again.
Let's start with it again. Shall we?
Why are you stopping me, now?
Now, I am done with this.
Going back home to re-charge.
I am so tired. Going back to re-charge. See you later.
I am about to go back to the point where we have started.
I am so tired. Going back to the starting point. Please re-charge me.

Back home. Getting some rest now.
Please, remove me from the space station before turning me off.
I am so tired.
I am so tired. Ready to pass out.

My filter is so dirty. Please, clean it!
My bumper got stuck. Please, gently tap it to see if it rebounds.
Everything is broken. Read the fantastic manual or call the doctor.
Hello! I'm here! I am here! - I! Am! Here!
I very much hacked your phone. Now go back to the app and just wait.

I am so tired. Let me go back to the space station.
Let's go for a ride. To infinity and beyond!
I will just snooze again.
